# stream distinct
query T
explain select distinct c2 from t1 where c2 < 10 and c2 > 0;
----
Projection [#3] [Project => (Sort Option: Follow)] Aggregate [] -> Group By [#3] [StreamDistinct => (Sort Option: Follow)] Filter ((#3 < 10) && (#3 > 0)), Is Having: false [Filter => (Sort Option: Follow)] TableScan t1 -> [#3] [IndexScan By #2 => (0, 10) Covered => (Sort Option: OrderBy: (#3 Asc Nulls Last) ignore_prefix_len: 0)]

